::DeathScythe::

DeathScythe takes the cup again, draining it in a few gulps and looking back 
at Zyber as she asks him his name. He didn't think his real name would go 
down well with a peaceful bot like that, a fake one would have to do.

"Name's Blaster," he says, taking the first name that came to mind, "Who are 
you?"
